      <lg xml:id="TolE0188">
<l>tānā meṉṉu makara viṟutiyum</l>
<l>yāme ṉiṟutiyu mataṉō raṉṉa</l>
<l>āey yāku yāme ṉiṟuti</l>
<l>yāvayiṉ yakaramey keṭutal vēṇṭu</l>
<l>mēṉai yiraṇṭu neṭumutal kuṟukum</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The ending of <foreign xml:lang="ta">num</foreign> has no change.<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">iyarkaiyākum</foreign> i.e. will have no empty-morph, e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">num-m-oṭu.</foreign> </note></l>
      </lg>
